article.description: — Karl Jones came off the bench to score 20 points and grab 12 rebounds and UNLV remained unbeaten with a 126-54 victory over Life Pacific on Saturday night.
article.headline: Jones posts double-double as UNLV routs Life Pacific 126-54
article.linkText: Jones posts double-double as UNLV routs Life Pacific 126-54
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- — Karl Jones came off the bench to score 20 points and grab 12 rebounds and UNLV remained unbeaten with a 126-54 victory over Life Pacific on Saturday night. Jones added 12 rebounds and three blocks for the Rebels (7-0). Jackie Johnson III scored 14 points on 6-of-8 shooting. Keshon Gilbert shot 4 for 5 and had 13 points. Albert Matute led the way for the Warriors with 13 points and two steals. Daniel Hernandez and Pedro Leal-Cruz scored eight apiece. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
